Withdraw funds from your account
Your earnings are credited to your Toloka account immediately after the requester accepts the task. Earnings are paid in dollars, and you can cash them in your local currency through PayPal, or Payoneer. Depending on where you live, you may also be able to withdraw money via QIWI. And Turkish citizens — through Papara.

Please note: this app is intended for users over the age of 18. Please read the license agreement before installing Toloka: https://toloka.ai/tolokers/legal/toloka_mobile_agreement
